vintage.name: Men's Suit Vintage & Custom Made
vintage.description: We are selling my Dad’s beautiful, vintage, custom-made double-breasted suit.  It is roughly a 48 jacket and the pants are 44.  However, since it was custom-made, it will be easy to alter.  As I remember, Dad had the suit designed in 1976 because he had three weddings to attend for his nephews and did not own a single good suit.  Dad passed in 1987 and his suit was stored in a closet until I rediscovered it a few weeks ago.  It was designed and made by Filian’s, a master custom tailor in San Francisco.  The original sales price in 1976 was $3,750, and the beautiful workmanship justifies the high cost.  It is a bargain at $750.  You are welcome to call me with questions.
